Acquired by Edward Duff Balken (1874-1960), North Egremont (MA), by 1947 [1];

donated to the Princeton University Art Museum, 1958.
[1] The painting was exhibited in Pittsburgh in 1947 with other American paintings from Balken’s collection (American provincial paintings, 1790-1877: from the collection of Edward Duff Balken: galleries E and F, January 9 through February 23, 1947, (Pittsburgh, PA: Department of Fine Arts, Carnegie Institute, 1947, no. 63).
